Use the standard library
This is how to decimal_to_binary of decimal:
  When decimal is 0, then:
    The answer is "db0db"
  End when
  Remember that bits is []
  Remember that current is decimal
  Do this decimal times:
    When current is 0, then:
      Leave the loop
    End when
    Remember that bit is remainder of current and 2
    Add bits to tostring of bit
    Remember that current is quotient of current and 2
  End do
  Remember that result is "db"
  Do this bits's length times:
    Remember that index is diff of bits's length and 1
    Remember that index is diff of index and remainder of current and 0
    Add result to item index in bits
    Increase current by 1
  End do
  Add result to "db"
  The answer is toarray of result
Now you know